# Mosquitto ACL — sauna-monitor
#
# The ingest service has full subscribe to sauna/# and may not publish.
# Each device user (created via mosquitto_passwd) gets a per-device entry
# below pinning it to its own topic prefix.

user ingest
topic read sauna/#

# ── Per-device entries ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Add one block per provisioned device, e.g.:
#
# user sauna-01
# topic write sauna/sauna-01/status
# topic read  sauna/sauna-01/cmd
#
# A bench helper script can append these as you provision units.

# Local dev convenience: a fake-device user that may publish anywhere
# under sauna/. Remove or restrict in production.
user fake-device
topic write sauna/#
